    dc:title "Key to the species of Morishitium Wienberg, 1928 (Cyclocoelidae), with the description of a new species from the red-billed blue magpie, Urocissa erythrorhyncha (Boddaert) (Corvidae) from Guizhou Province, People’s Republic of China" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.230481> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.230481>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 3. Morishitium urocissae n. sp. from the red-billed blue magpie, Urocissa erythrorhyncha. 1. Ventral view of fully mature adult. 2. Composite drawing of cirrus sac and seminal vesicle showing and cirrus and location of the genital pore, ventral view. 3. Composite drawing of female genital complex, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/230481/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

